How I contour my lips! 
Step 1: Prep‚Äô your lips
Exfoliate with a warm towel
Hydrate with lip balm
Blot excess oil 
Step 2: Line your lips
Define cupid‚Äôs bow with an X
Line the center-bottom
Continue lining the shape of your lips
*Pro tip: Overline cupid‚Äôs bow to create fuller lips
Fill lips with color

Step 3: Contour!
Outline with a darker shade
Create depth in the inner corners
Draw vertical lines to add dimension
*Pro tip: Correct with concealer
Blend with lip balm
Mattify with tissue
